data.description: Adorable 2 bedroom 2.5 bath updated townhome in desirable Orchard Gate subdivision. The kitchen features white cabinetry, quartz countertops, tile backsplash, pantry and breakfast bar overlooking the combination living and dining spaces. The second floor offers large primary suite with plenty of closet space and an updated ensuite bathroom, as well as second bathroom and bedroom with walk in closet. The fully finished basement features additional living space and tons of extra storage. Outside you will find a huge deck with an awesome green space view, perfect for entertaining. This move in ready unit is located close to schools, shopping, restaurants and transportation.
